summary: pobwes                                 ‘pune wns rer Saari cop’ (Saari police) Pune: “Pune is a city in Finland.” Pobwe: “The city is in the north of Finland, near the town of Hiiya. It is named after the city of Punpunahti, which is on the island of Puna. Paunahta: "Puna is an island in northern Finland." Punahto:  "The island is made up of many small islands, many of which are uninhabited. These islands are known as Puninaht, or 'Puni'
